## Key Features
- **Risk scoring algorithm**: Weighted from clinical inputs (yellowing, sclera, preterm, weight, phototherapy history)
- **Processing pipeline animation**: 4-step animated analysis with progress bar
- **Color-coded risk**: Green (Low) / Amber (Moderate) / Red (High) throughout all screens
- **6 mock history records** pre-loaded with different risk levels + filter chips
- **Yes/No medical toggles**, delivery type and feeding type selectors
- **Auto age calculation** from date/time of birth
- **Save flow**: Saves to in-memory history, navigates home with toast confirmation
- **Animated scan line** in camera preview; pulsing capture button ring
